thread.title: BRIEF-Biogaia Q4 profit rises, proposes extra dividend

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Biogaia Q4 profit rises, proposes extra dividend
text:
Feb 8 (Reuters) - Biogaia AB:
* Q4 NET SALES AMOUNTED TO SEK 170.1 MILLION VS YR-AGO 138.8 MILLION, AN INCREASE OF 23% (EXCLUDING FOREIGN EXCHANGE EFFECTS, 27%)
* Q4 OPERATING PROFIT WAS SEK 64.7 MILLION VS YR-AGO 46.4 MILLION
* SAYS PROPOSES THAT UPCOMING AGM ON APRIL 25, 2018, APPROVE AN ORDINARY DIVIDEND OF SEK 4.31 (YR-AGO 3.16) PER SHARE AND AN EXTRAORDINARY DIVIDEND OF SEK 4.69 (YR-AGO 4.34) PER SHARE Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
